    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Scenario 3",
    "long_instructions": "*Review the scenario below and use the AI Chat to learn more in-depth about this threat:*\r\n\r\n## Scenario 3\r\n\r\nThe Secretary of the Student Government creates a Google Form for Class President elections. It’s stored in a folder with edit access for the whole grade instead of just the student government officers. \r\n\r\nA curious 10th grader who is not on Student Government finds she can edit the form questions and responses. She tells her friends who decide to add joke candidates and change existing responses. \r\n\r\nThe integrity of the election is compromised.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://images.code.org/8dc766dc9680e6d458cc2c44d218c559-image-1752771663262.00.40 PM.png\" alt=\"computer \" width=\"300\"/>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Chat with an Expert: Security Auditor\r\n\r\nA **security auditor** evaluates an organization’s systems, policies, and configurations to identify weaknesses and ensure compliance with security standards.\r\n",
